the Ryo I knew.

104
00:07:07,660 --> 00:07:11,164
Kaori, who is that woman? She's beautiful.

105
00:07:11,164 --> 00:07:14,292
Ryo's old friend.

106
00:07:14,467 --> 00:07:20,997
Why don't you sit down? Your drink,
Bloody Mary, okay, as usual?

107
00:07:21,340 --> 00:07:23,543
I'll take it if there's no poison in it.

108
