be next year?

118
00:08:07,653 --> 00:08:10,623
Hey! Why next year?!

119
00:08:10,623 --> 00:08:14,727
Oh, right. How old is Saeba now?
When is your birthday?

120
00:08:14,727 --> 00:08:18,097
Well, if you have mokkori with me,
I'll tell you.

121
00:08:18,097 --> 00:08:20,933
