everything about Ryo.

135
00:09:15,021 --> 00:09:17,557
I don't know anything about him.

136
00:09:17,557 --> 00:09:20,720
I didn't even know he was in the US before.

137
00:09:21,027 --> 00:09:24,929
Because Ryo doesn't know his birthday.

138
00:09:25,565 --> 00:09:27,533
