you did and said!

141
00:09:34,874 --> 00:09:39,312
Hey, don't be so loud. I've got a hangover.

142
00:09:39,312 --> 00:09:43,214
Listen, don't say anything about our past
in front of Kaori, never ever!

143
00:09:44,984 --> 00:09:47,019
