144
00:09:47,019 --> 00:09:49,255
She's your assistant, isn't she?

145
00:09:49,255 --> 00:09:51,155
She can know about you, can't she?

146
00:09:52,058 --> 00:09:55,561
Well, I don't think it's a good idea to
bring up the old stories

147
00:09:55,561 --> 00:09:57,463
